{"type": "article", "id": 33797, "title": "Hugo Boss 要专注做男装，以及，今年秋冬最好看的球鞋有这15双 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-27T02:46:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13396, "name": "sneaker"}, {"id": 34359, "name": "伦敦 Crepe City"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 2910, "name": "Hugo Boss"}, {"id": 3573, "name": "BoF"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 34360, "name": "Zenith"}, {"id": 34361, "name": "Land Rover"}, {"id": 906, "name": "川久保玲"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 105, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161027101115s6ryERAYonbDkeK5.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/hugo-boss-ceo-says-wants-to-abandon-luxury-segment\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Hugo Boss 欲放弃奢侈品市场，专注于男装线</b></a> | 据德国品牌 Hugo Boss 的首席执行官 Mark Langer 所称，品牌将放弃一部分奢侈品市场，重新回归到男装线上。最近的一个计划是要关闭一些不盈利的店铺以减少约 5500 万美元的固定成本。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/bof-and-topshop-launch-future-voices-to-nurture-young-fashion-talent\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>时尚传媒 BoF 和 Topshop 联手，发起培养年轻设计师的计划</b></a> | 近日，时尚传媒 The Bussiness of Fashion 已要与英国高街品牌 Topshop 签订长期合约，共同推出名为 Future VOICES 的青年设计师培养计划。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/sonia-rykiel-shutter-secondary-line-lay-off-quarter-of-staff-eric-langon-10691160/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Sonia Rykiel 要砍掉副线品牌</b></a> | 法国设计师同名品牌 Sonia Rykiel 要砍掉其副线品牌 Sonia by Sonia Rykiel，并裁掉近四分之一的员工，集中精力发展主线品牌 Sonia Rykiel。此外，该公司还计划推出更低价的产品，以适应更加激烈的市场竞争。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>川久保玲 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/comme-des-garcons-homme-plus-day-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">COMME des GARÇONS Homme Plus </a>发布最新的 Day Pack 系列，该系列采用了轻量耐用的尼龙材质，共有四款配色，两个大小，定价分别为 17000 及 19000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092452l5H3EmQLr8sNhSXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092506b7BSXMOuJwFsHEL6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092506XQYBRZEVxfNl710W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Vans 的 2016 秋冬 Sk8-Hi 鞋款还不错，该系列融合了全粒面皮革以及仿蛇皮等特殊的材质，更有“吸睛”的金属元素。现已登陆<a href=\"http://www.vans.com/shop/vans-combo-sk8-hi?cm_mmc=LinkShare-_-Affiliate-_-je6NUbpObpQ-_-335851&amp;utm_source=linkshare&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=je6NUbpObpQ&amp;ranMID=24747&amp;ranEAID=je6NUbpObpQ&amp;ranLinkID=10-1&amp;ranSiteID=je6NUbpObpQ-.cHj4SbY3ebSK1OcSQcx8w\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610270925264K5UVGIABweikZHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092540sYoFMKx6eNGS7VBh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092540GfHD2Ro3OALxWyzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092540YCB4Ab9ysPxefvQX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092540Kb2UR9kFYqpH1Au8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092540PimzkC97xGruMyjd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610270925401PiksN60etaSZFWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">作为伦敦最大的球鞋交易市场，Crepe City 每年的盛会也会吸引全英国的潮人前去参与。在线生活方式杂志<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/10/25/crepe-city-2016-best-sneakers/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Highsnobiety </a>就评出了今年秋冬 Crepe City 上面最好看的十五双 Sneaker，来看看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092602mp7nUqINRBhxToDE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092620xq4r1WcJeXnogGEP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092620qG46lEXCrM3OAJjx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610270926225NRDiOAqX7pwfSha.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092622XrjbENL1A5RvlVWp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092622afxCrsNB5LqO2i0Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092622tC1Avs3b5TrOcNHZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092636d8DiJFqtWs62HXC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092636F1Y0ONaJ5Ryv7Kxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092652I9aMqn436hryRFLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092652ZpCMPImNynDgEekG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092652QyZT3jUqICSJksKv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092653btYjDNdRzZSh8sLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610271425474MIBuh0SW8UyVTAq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027142752qdmzJKYgtx4HSZOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">创立于 2002 年的洛杉矶潮牌 Opening Ceremony 与美国最大的飞行夹克和军用品供应商  Alpha Industries 联手，带来了全新的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/opening-ceremony-alpha-industries-flight-jackets-editorial\" rel=\"nofollow\">  Alpha Industries MA-1 </a>飞行员夹克。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092713EtFkB4bDqOxpTX1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665996\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092723IDaoARzimfH39Ejh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665996\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092723TXP72ReDgcvLlYGH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610270927238ynrZ4ohQ56C7JRD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665996\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092723V9fyY084w6KaRTgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665996\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092731MvLsHQICy4hqG5rg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092731k463XGWoDsIKzRiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610270927390qVhHTtAa94Cney1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">瑞士手表品牌 Zenith 与 Land Rover 首次合作，推出了名为 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/10/26/zenith-land-rover-watch-partnership/#slide-4\" rel=\"nofollow\">El Primero Range Rover </a>的限量款手表。&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016102709283714R9eiYhabsq0Ldj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161027092847fFweR4Zor8IhGOUD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610270928555nOLzuVclBRtk793.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610270929021q9Kn5460sHhQNkP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}